### List todos
GET {{baseUrl}}/students?page=0&size=10&sort=nome,asc

### List by name
GET {{baseUrl}}/students?name=joao&page=0&size=10&sort=name,asc

### List by city
GET {{baseUrl}}/students?city=Criciúma&page=0&size=10&sort=name,asc

### List by city
GET {{baseUrl}}/students?state=SC&page=0&size=10&sort=name,asc

### List by email
GET {{baseUrl}}/students?email=joao@email.com&page=0&size=10&sort=name,asc


### Monthly Billing - Faturamento mensal
GET {{baseUrl}}/reports/monthlyBilling

### Students By City
GET {{baseUrl}}/reports/studentsByCity

### Outstanding Invoices - Faturas em aberto
GET {{baseUrl}}/reports/outstandingInvoices